high_descs: Turn around to the left and check the sink, then resume to walk toward the bathroom straight ahead.
Enter the bathroom and retrieve the keychain in front of an apple in the sink.

Turn around to exit the bathroom, then turn right and walk down the hallway and turn right to enter the room on the end on the right side; upon entering the room, walk toward the dresser ahead bearing right.
Put the keychain on the top of the dresser and in its front left corner.
Turn around to exit the room, then turn left to go to the room on the left at the end of hallway; upon entering the room, walk toward the desk on the right.
Retrieve the keychain behind the spray dispenser on the desk.

Turn around to exit the room, then turn right and walk down the hallway and turn right to enter the room on the end on the right side; upon entering the room, walk toward the dresser ahead bearing right.
Put the keychain behind the other keychain on the top of the dresser.
anns.task_desc: Gather the two KeyChains and put them over the Dresser.

high_descs: Turn around and move towards the sink.
Take the keychain from the sink in the toilet.
Turn back and move to the room with the dresser.
Place the keychain on the dresser.
Turn back,walk through the door and take left towards the desk in the bedroom.
Take the keychain from the table.
Move back towards the dresser.
Put the keychain next to the first key on the dresser.
anns.task_desc: Collectively place the KeyChain on the Dresser.

high_descs: Go forward into the bathroom straight ahead and go to the bathroom sink.
Pick up the keychain on the sink.
Leave the room and go down the hall to the last dresser on the right and enter.
Place the keychain on the dresser.
Leave the room and take a left down the hallway and then the last left into the room and go to the desk.
Pick up the keychain on the table.
Leave the room take a right and then into the dresser the last on the right.
Put the keychain on the dresser.
anns.task_desc: Place two sets of KeyChain on a Dresser.
